    <!-- About CodeIgniter Development -->
    <section class="about-codeigniter">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Why Choose CodeIgniter for Your Projects?</h2>
            <p>
                CodeIgniter is a lightweight PHP framework known for its speed, simplicity, and flexibility. At Quickly Platforms, we specialize in delivering CodeIgniter-based solutions for web applications, APIs, and more.
            </p>
            <p>
