                    <p>Leverage CodeIgniter's built-in libraries for email, session management, and more.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Security</h3>
                    <p>Ensure robust security with CodeIgniter's built-in protection against CSRF and XSS attacks.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Database Support</h3>
                    <p>Integrate with multiple databases like MySQL, PostgreSQL, and SQLite.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Custom Development</h3>
                    <p>Create tailored solutions to meet your specific business requirements.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
